talk1 = Array[String](["Why are there so many spikes everywhere???", "We constantly have to keep an eye out for them, they're all over the top of the city.", "And if we fall into them, we have to flee so we don't get killed by them.", "It takes a moment to get back up, but by then, you'll already have gone into the next room.", "I just don't see the point of it."])
